# API Base URL Configuration
# 
# The API URL is now runtime-configurable. It will:
# 1. Use window.__API_BASE_URL__ if set (inject via script tag in index.html)
# 2. Use VITE_API_BASE_URL if set here (for development)
# 3. Auto-detect from current hostname (for production)
# 4. Default to http://localhost:8000
#
# For local development, uncomment the line below:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000
#
# For remote API access during development, set it to your API server:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://your-api-ip:8000
#
# Note: In production, the API URL will auto-detect from the frontend's hostname
